<li><span class="citation book">DuBose, James (2008). <i>Searching for Sparta: A 40-year Retrospective on the Movie</i> In the Heat of the Night (2nd ed.). lulu.com.</span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AIn+the+Heat+of+the+Night+%28film%29&amp;rft.au=DuBose%2C+James&amp;rft.aufirst=James&amp;rft.aulast=DuBose&amp;rft.btitle=Searching+for+Sparta%3A+A+40-year+Retrospective+on+the+Movie+In+the+Heat+of+the+Night&amp;rft.date=2008&amp;rft.edition=2nd&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.pub=lulu.com&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
